reviewText: I got this as a gift for a family member who likes action and adventure films and he responded that he really appreciated the many fine films combined in this package
Title: 10-Movie Action Pack V.2

reviewText: All of the films are action packed and interesting-however-there are at least 3 Chuck Norris films side by side-as much as I like Chuck Norris-there needs to be some comic relief in the midst of it all-his films are very high adventure with quite a bit of violence-and three in a row is a bit much.
Title: 10-Movie Action Pack V.2

reviewText: Near class B movies. some good acting, but certainly entertaining if you don't expect too much. If you like action this is for you.

reviewText: For my Brothers Birthday, I got him this DVD. it wasn't the only git I got him but a nice little addition. He loved it! He prefers sometimes the multimovie pack and is a fan of older movies from the 1980's or before, and his was a treasuretrove of enjoyment for him. I'm not as much an action film fan and find many 1980's era films rather silly but, hey, it worked for him so I'm happy.
